  <brief_title>Phase I Trial From GRID 18F-FDG-PET Biological Imaging-guided Intensitymodulated Radiotherapy (BG-IMRT) With Patients With Recurrent or New Head or Neck Tumor in Previously Radiated Area</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase I Trial From GRID 18F-FDG-PET Biological Imaging-guided Intensitymodulated Radiotherapy (BG-IMRT) With Patients With Recurrent or New Head or Neck Tumor in Previously Radiated Area</official_title>
