  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trials examines the feasibility of GRID-therapy combined with biologically imaging based
      IMRT (BG-IMRT). Within this trial, the strict toxicity parameters of primary treatment of
      head and neck tumors are used. The GRID and BG-IMRT technique might be possible to reduce the
      total radiation dose 2 to 3 times.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
